{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 3 The LEAP window displays a physics task related to Newton's cradle.",
    "Students can submit their responses in the \"Answer\" box and send it to the LLM for feedback.",
    "The complexity of the feedback -\"low\", \"middle\", or \"high\"-can be selected by the student based on their preference",
    "The LEAP application integrates LLMs to facilitate seamless interaction between the system and the AI models.",
    "As mentioned before, while the language models offered by OpenAI are currently the only LLMs available for users, the platform is designed to support additional LLMs in the future."
  ]
}